  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Higher education restructuring regime (HERR)
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A scheme for higher education providers in England facing financial difficulties as a result of coronavirus (COVID-19).</p>

  </div>
</div>

